metadata.name: Free Falling
metadata.description:
"Free Falling" is a piece that wants to speak to your inner, innocent and carefree self.
Is a piece made for everyone who values being free from  any type of chain that holds our most autenthic self from emerging and rising in life.
Is a piece for everyone feeling lost who need to find the spark and motivation to move on.
"Free Falling" is a very personal piece that wants you to be free and happy in life.

Created by ejoloo from January 12- February 20, 2022
Clip Studio Paint
3508x2480 px
